data.description: Welcome to the ultimate paradise awaiting your presence! Nestled on an expansive one-acre lot, this captivating property is a haven of possibilities. Imagine yourself basking in the beauty of your private fenced yard, complete with a dog run for your furry friends to frolic freely. Entertain guests around the inviting firepit, sharing stories under the starlit sky. But that's not all – this home is a hobbyist's dream come true. A detached garage or workshop beckons the creative spirit in you, offering limitless potential for crafting, DIY projects, or storage. And with the included riding lawn mower, maintaining this picturesque landscape is a breeze. Safety and convenience seamlessly blend as the home boasts a top-tier security system with integrated cameras, ensuring peace of mind. Not to mention, all appliances are thoughtfully included, making moving in a breeze. Your oasis awaits! Schedule a showing today to experience the life you've envisioned. Your new adventure begins here.
